  </style>

  <div class="container">
    <div style="background:rgba(196,149,106,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(196,149,106,0.25);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem 1.5rem;font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      🧳 <strong style="color:#C4956A;">Airlines lost 7.6 million bags last year.</strong> With baggage fees up to $45/bag and carry-on rules getting stricter, packing smart saves money and stress. Generate your custom checklist below. <a href="https://gab.ae/news/currency-volatility-oil-crisis-travel-budgets-2026" style="color:#C4956A;">Travel costs are shifting →</a>
    </div>
    <header>
      <h1>Packing List Generator</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Generate a customized <strong>travel packing checklist</strong> based on your destination, trip length, and travel style. Check off items as you pack, add your own, and print when ready.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>Packing for a trip doesn't have to mean last-minute panic and forgotten chargers. This <strong>packing list generator</strong> builds a personalized <strong>travel packing checklist</strong> tailored to where you're going, how long you'll be away, and how you like to travel. Whether you're a minimalist backpacker or a checked-luggage maximalist, you'll get exactly <strong>what to pack</strong> — nothing more, nothing less.</p>
        <p>Your progress saves automatically to your browser, so you can come back and keep checking items off. Add custom items, print your <strong>packing checklist</strong>, or reset and start fresh for your next adventure.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Generator Config -->
